    For width == 64, this can represent 2^64.                                   
                                                                                
    Recommendation                                                              
                                                                                
    Fix the function by clarifying its intended semantics and avoiding invalid  
    shifts.                                                                     
                                                                                
    If it is meant to return the high bit mask for a width-bit value, use:      
                                                                                
                                                                                
     #include <stdint.h>                                                        
